    {
      "id": "el_26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 828,
      "width": 368,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: All cats are animals -> cats inside animals\nStep 2: Every cat is an animal (guaranteed)\nStep 3: But not every animal is a cat\n\n  ┌──────────────┐\n  │ B (Animals)  │\n  │ ┌──────────┐ │\n  │ │ A (Cats) │ │\n  │ └──────────┘ │\n  └──────────────┘\n\nTRICK:\nA-type -> converse is I-type only.\nAll A are B -> Some B are A (NEVER All B are A)\n\nAnswer: Some B are A follows ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 26,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: All cats are animals -> cats inside animals\nStep 2: Every cat is an animal (guaranteed)\nStep 3: But not every animal is a cat\n\n  ┌──────────────┐\n  │ B (Animals)  │\n  │ ┌──────────┐ │\n  │ │ A (Cats) │ │\n  │ └──────────┘ │\n  └──────────────┘\n\nTRICK:\nA-type -> converse is I-type only.\nAll A are B -> Some B are A (NEVER All B are A)\n\nAnswer: Some B are A follows ✓",
