    {
      "id": "el_31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 828,
      "width": 317,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Some overlap between A and B\nStep 2: Part of A is in B, part outside\nStep 3: Cannot conclude All or No\n\n  ┌────┐  ┌────┐\n  │ A  ├──┤ B  │\n  │    │XX│    │\n  └────┘  └────┘\n\nTRICK:\nI-type converts to I-type.\nSome A are B -> Some B are A (always valid).\nNever upgrade to All!\n\nAnswer: Some B are A follows ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3100,
