      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Some overlap between A and B\nStep 2: Part of A is in B, part outside\nStep 3: Cannot conclude All or No\n\n  ┌────┐  ┌────┐\n  │ A  ├──┤ B  │\n  │    │XX│    │\n  └────┘  └────┘\n\nTRICK:\nI-type converts to I-type.\nSome A are B -> Some B are A (always valid).\nNever upgrade to All!\n\nAnswer: Some B are A follows ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
