    {
      "id": "el_36",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 828,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: No overlap between dogs and cats\nStep 2: Completely separate circles\nStep 3: Symmetric: No B are A also true\n\n  ┌────┐    ┌────┐\n  │ A  │    │ B  │\n  │    │    │    │\n  └────┘    └────┘\n\nTRICK:\nE-type converts to E-type.\nNo A are B -> No B are A (symmetric).\n\"Some A are B\" contradicts this!\n\nAnswer: No B are A follows ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
