      "groupIds": [
        "type_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: No overlap between dogs and cats\nStep 2: Completely separate circles\nStep 3: Symmetric: No B are A also true\n\n  ┌────┐    ┌────┐\n  │ A  │    │ B  │\n  │    │    │    │\n  └────┘    └────┘\n\nTRICK:\nE-type converts to E-type.\nNo A are B -> No B are A (symmetric).\n\"Some A are B\" contradicts this!\n\nAnswer: No B are A follows ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
