    {
      "id": "el_46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1255,
      "width": 332,
      "height": 288,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Some pens overlap with pencils\nStep 2: All pencils are inside erasers\nStep 3: Overlapping part is inside erasers too\n\n  ┌──────────────┐\n  │ C (Erasers)  │\n  │ ┌──────────┐ │\n  │ │B(Pencil) │ │\n  └─│──┌──┐────│─┘\n    └──│XX│────┘\n  ┌────│  │──┐\n  │ A  └──┘  │ (Pens)\n  └──────────┘\n\nTRICK:\nI+A=I. Some+All = Some.\nNever upgrades to All!\n\nAnswer: Some pens are erasers ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
