      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Some pens overlap with pencils\nStep 2: All pencils are inside erasers\nStep 3: Overlapping part is inside erasers too\n\n  ┌──────────────┐\n  │ C (Erasers)  │\n  │ ┌──────────┐ │\n  │ │B(Pencil) │ │\n  └─│──┌──┐────│─┘\n    └──│XX│────┘\n  ┌────│  │──┐\n  │ A  └──┘  │ (Pens)\n  └──────────┘\n\nTRICK:\nI+A=I. Some+All = Some.\nNever upgrades to All!\n\nAnswer: Some pens are erasers ✓",
