    {
      "id": "el_56",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1725,
      "width": 332,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Some artists overlap singers\nStep 2: No singers overlap dancers\nStep 3: That part of artists cannot be dancers\n\n  ┌────────┐\n  │A(Artist)│\n  │ ┌──┐   │   ┌────────┐\n  │ │XX│   │   │C(Dance) │\n  └─│──│───┘   └─────────┘\n    │B │ (Singers)\n    └──┘\n\nTRICK:\nI+E=O. Some+No = Some-not.\nO-type CANNOT be converted!\n\nAnswer: Some artists not dancers ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
