    {
      "id": "el_71",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2151,
      "width": 317,
      "height": 288,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A inside B inside C -> All A are C ✓\nStep 2: D overlaps C, but may not touch A\nStep 3: Some A are D: NOT definite\n\n  ┌──────────────────┐\n  │ C       ┌───┐   │\n  │ ┌─────┐ │ D │   │\n  │ │ B   │ └───┘   │\n  │ │ ┌─┐ │         │\n  │ │ │A│ │         │\n  │ │ └─┘ │         │\n  │ └─────┘         │\n  └──────────────────┘\n\nTRICK:\nChain All first (A+A=A). Then check Some.\nAll+Some = NO definite conclusion.\n\nAnswer: Only \"All A are C\" follows ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 71,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A inside B inside C -> All A are C ✓\nStep 2: D overlaps C, but may not touch A\nStep 3: Some A are D: NOT definite\n\n  ┌──────────────────┐\n  │ C       ┌───┐   │\n  │ ┌─────┐ │ D │   │\n  │ │ B   │ └───┘   │\n  │ │ ┌─┐ │         │\n  │ │ │A│ │         │\n  │ │ └─┘ │         │\n  │ └─────┘         │\n  └──────────────────┘\n\nTRICK:\nChain All first (A+A=A). Then check Some.\nAll+Some = NO definite conclusion.\n\nAnswer: Only \"All A are C\" follows ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
